      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SONG BY FERNANDO (4) flew the lids with a fast early split but ran over at the finish when a narrow sixth (17.37) over 300m at this track. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Ready to return to form. PAW BAUTISTA (8) has been hard to follow lately, running sixth (22.86) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at Shepparton. Expected to do much better this time. EXTREME DASH (7) hit the ground running from out wide and was on speed early but swamped late when 6th at Ballarat in a T3 RSTW. One of the main contenders. PINK MOSCATO (3) deserves plenty of thought at her first run at this circuit.",
